Industry News


                Career & Workplace            


Minneapolis exec joins Accenture C-suite




Jan 14, 2014, 11:09am CST






Industries & Tags


                    Career & Workplace,                 


            Accounting & Consulting             








Jim Hammerand


                            Digital Editor                        

Minneapolis / St. Paul Business Journal














                    Share
                


























